INSERT INTO `sk_comments` VALUES (1,1,'A WordPress Commenter','wapuu@wordpress.example','https://wordpress.org/','','2020-05-06 16:53:44','2020-05-06 16:53:44','Hi, this is a comment.\nTo get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.\nCommenter avatars come from <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.',0,'1','','',0,0),(2,157,'Patrick Callahan','meks1@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 10:53:23','2015-11-24 10:53:23','I have spent some great time there, too. You post returned me to this awesome road-trip that me and my girlfriend had back in 2011. Keep up the good work John, looking forward to your new posts.',0,'1','','',0,0),(3,157,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:03:54','2015-11-24 11:03:54','Your road-trip was awesome, too. I have heard some stories on how you swim with dolphins. Sea was warm, sand was there - heaven on Earth.',0,'1','','',2,0),(4,157,'John Bergstein','meks3@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:10:32','2015-11-24 11:10:32','Just a quick note on this road-trip diary - beaches that we visited where completely abandoned and wild. \r\nThere was no water so we could\\\'t make any shower. We have to wait for return home.\r\n\r\nBeside that, we had really really good time here and I wish that one day you visit this magic place, too.',0,'1','','',0,0),(5,157,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:19:05','2015-11-24 11:19:05','I couldn’t agree more with you John! Thanks for sharing this brilliant article!',0,'1','','',0,0),(6,157,'John Bergstein','meks3@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:26:17','2015-11-24 11:26:17','You are welcome Lisa, really appreciate it.',0,'1','','',5,0),(7,191,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:07:14','2015-11-24 11:07:14','This site makes me hungry.\r\n\r\nBeside this your site looks pretty awesome, super feeling when I\\\'m browsing posts. Everything runs and loads fast and smooth.',0,'1','','',0,0),(8,192,'Patrick Callahan','meks1@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 10:56:12','2015-11-24 10:56:12','This is why i\\\'d rather have a green and red scarf. Next to keeping my scarfs in-house I keep them in separate house. Unfortunately I can wear them only when its winter - summer is bit warm for scarfs :)\r\n\r\nI hope that you agree with me',0,'1','','',0,0),(9,192,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:02:12','2015-11-24 11:02:12','I agree with you - I also keep my scarves in one special place. I wear them only when its winter and winters here can be vary vary cold.',0,'1','','',8,0),(10,192,'John Bergstein','meks3@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:11:44','2015-11-24 11:11:44','I change my set of scarves every year. Sometimes it costs me a lot of money but when scarves are in question I simply just don\\\'t care.',0,'1','','',0,0),(11,192,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:23:32','2015-11-24 11:23:32','I will share this article on all my social networks - you can follow me there Patrick.',0,'1','','',0,0),(12,197,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:05:08','2015-11-24 11:05:08','Currently, I\\\'m on golf crash course - day 7. Wish me luck John :)\r\nI hope that I won\\\'t hurt anyone.',0,'1','','',0,0),(13,203,'Patrick Callahan','meks1@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 10:58:52','2015-11-24 10:58:52','Blueberry pie is something that I would like to eat on every-day basic. I’ve been having a blueberry moment and it’s not over yet.  Blueberry Pancakes and Blueberry Jam, sure. Blueberry Syrup, Blueberry Ice Cream and Blueberry-Buttermilk, Blueberry Pie and many more.\r\n\r\nAnd yeah I have a quick word on the sugar – start with the lesser amount and taste.  Now that blueberries are truly in season, you might not want completely full amount.',0,'1','','',0,0),(14,203,'Lisa Scholfield','meks2@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:00:39','2015-11-24 11:00:39','OK, I\\\'m hungry now - Blueberry pie recipe for the win!',0,'1','','',0,0),(15,203,'John Bergstein','meks3@mekshq.com','https://mekshq.com/','178.148.175.112','2015-11-24 11:13:03','2015-11-24 11:13:03','One day I will prepare my recipes for my website readers - I think that could be awesome thing to do.',0,'1','','',14,0);
